==Finnish==
{{Finnish index|pe}}

===Etymology===
derives from the name of the Baltic god of thunder

===Noun===
'''perkele'''

#The [[Devil]], [[Satan]]
#[[devil]]

====Synonyms====
*[[paholainen]]
*[[piru]]

===Interjection===
'''perkele!'''

#(''vulgar'') an interjection said by someone for example annoyed or surprised
#:''perkele se on hidas!'' (damn it's slow!)

===Adjective===
'''perkele'''

#(''vulgar'') an [[intensifier]]
#:''se on perkeleen ruma'' (it is damn ugly)

